* Kowalski, Bob. &quot;Douglas XTB2D-1 Skypirate&quot; (Naval Fighters, Volume Thirty-Six). Simi Valley, CA: Ginter Books, 1996. .
*Wagner, Ray. &quot;American Combat Airplanes of the 20th Century: A Comprehensive Reference&quot;. Reno, Nevada: Jack Bacon &amp; Co., 2004. </text><links>
